<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>MONONA PROTESTS. MONONA DEFENDS THE CONSTITUTION AND DEMOCRACY

We the People Are Pissed! Resistance is growing. Protests are growing. The 

Giant is rising. Peacefully, non-violently, but with determination.

