<h3>Signs of Solidarity - Business Canvass Training</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, April 2, 2026 at 2:30 PM UTC - 3:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Chapbook Cafe at Schuler Books<br>2660 28th St SE suite G<br>Grand Rapids, MI 49512</p>
