<h3>Ripon Resisters Wednesday Rotary Square Rally</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, March 25, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 9:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Ripon Town (Rotary) Square<br>100 Watson St<br>Ripon, WI 54971</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We&apos;re here on the corner of Watson and Jackson, hoping others will join us to show visibility to:
●Stop ICE&apos;s aggressive attacks on immigrants and citizens. 
●Defund ICE to reasonable levels.
●End Trump&apos;s dictator rule.
●Restore the balance of the three branches of government. 
●Protect the freedom of the press. 
●Stop the politicization of the DOJ.
●Stop invading/attacking other countries.
●Fund Medicaid, research, education, parks, social programs.
●Etc.

This a local Indivisible event!

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
