<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Our goal is to make the Ann Arbor NO KINGS 3 rally and march the largest yet!  And we hope it will be part of the largest protest in the history of the USA!   Come to our non-violent event to say NO to ICE, NO the war against Iran, and NO to kings in the USA!  We are helping to build a massive, non-violent, pro-democracy movement that can slow, block and defeat Trump.  You can be part of it!

