    <Placemark>
        <name>MMOP Signature Collection @ No Kings Romulus</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>MMOP Signature Collection @ No Kings Romulus</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>7525 Cogswell St<br>Romulus, MI 48174</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Michiganders for Money Out of Politics</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>All hands on deck to get corporate money out of state politics! Gather signatures for the Michiganders for Money out of Politics petition from folks attending the No Kings rally at:
 
Proposed Romulus ICE Detention Center
7525 Cogswell St
Romulus, MI 48174

https://www.mobilize.us/nokings/event/917339/


The rally officially runs from [START TIME] to [END TIME], and we will be collecting from [START TIME PRIOR TO EVENT] to [END TIME].

[**Mop Up Michigan**](http://mopupmichigan.org) would transform state politics by banning utilities and large state contractors from donating to the Michigan politicians who should be regulating and overseeing them. It would also close the largest dark money loophole in state law (the issue ad loophole). Getting this on the ballot and winning would be putting power back in the hands of the people!

All are welcome to help regardless of petition circulating experience! If you haven&apos;t volunteered before, please sign up at [**MopUpMichigan.org**](http://mopupmichigan.org). If you are in need of petitions or other supplies please check the box when you register and we will get you set up!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/927403/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
