<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> NE Oakland Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE is breaking the law and making our communities unsafe. Make a pledge to tell the Oakland County Board of Commissioners that we expect them to take every action available to protect our residents and public servants and to ensure all of us can access government services without fear of violence or intimidation. When you sign up, you&apos;ll receive a link to the latest call and email scripts in support of a resolution to keep ICE Out of OC!

Click [here](https://www.mobilize.us/neoaklandindivisible/event/922060/) to sign up to attend the next BOC meeting and to give and/or witness public testimony. When we show up, we win!</p>
