        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Coffee and Conversation w/ Abdi Daisane: St. Cloud State</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, March 26, 2026 at 8:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Atwood Memorial Center<br>651 1st St S<br>St. Cloud, MN 56301</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Minnesota DFL</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join DFL-endorsed candidate for State House District 14A, Abdi Daisane and DFL Community Organizer, Sam Brewer for this lowkey event at Red and Black Coffee in the Atwood Memorial Center on the SCSU campus with a focus on building community during these turbulent times (SCSU students are encouraged to attend, but other community members are welcome as well!). Got a news article you want to share? Want to chat about ways that we can make a difference in 2026? Want to ask Sam what his favorite flavor of ice cream is? (it&apos;s mint chocolate chip). Come grab some coffee, tea, or a pastry and support a great local business in the company of like-minded neighbors. Feel free to join for the whole time or just stop in for a few minutes!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/907989/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
