<h3>NO KINGS Vermillion</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 11:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Starting at corner of E Cherry and N Pine - Ending at Ratingen Platz<br>5 S Market St<br>Vermillion, SD 57069</p>
