        <name>NO KINGS Joplin, MO</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS Joplin, MO</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Old Big Lots parking lot<br>South Rangeline Road &amp; East 7th Street<br>Joplin, MO 64801</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## While families across America are struggling with sky-high prices for groceries, rent, and healthcare — the basics that keep slipping further out of reach — Donold †®ump is pouring billions of public dollars into militarized IÇE raids. We’re seeing masked agents snatching people off the streets, neighbors disappearing, and rights disappearing with them.

Now, as of February 28, he has doubled down on a dangerous new war of choice with Iran, launching joint strikes, escalating regional conflict, and putting service members and civilians in harm’s way instead of investing in the communities he’s supposed to serve. Bombs and power grabs abroad will not put food on tables or keep families safe at home.
 That’s not leadership. That is fear and control — the behavior of someone who wants to rule, not serve. A president answers to the people; a monarch answers to no one. †®ump is acting more like a king who hoards power than a public servant bound by law. America does not have kings — and our rally draws the line.

 This is a peaceful, family-friendly event — part of the nationwide NO KINGS day of action. Together, our multiracial coalition is standing up to say enough: we will not trade democracy for one man’s ego. We will lift our voices, hold our signs and flags high, and share stories from families living the impact of †®ump’s cruelty. High energy. Zero violence. Just unshakable resolve.
 
**We are coming together to:**
- **Reject** †®ump’s power grabs that sideline Congress, the courts, and the will of the people — from illegal war escalations to attacks on our rights at home.
- **Defend** our communities from IÇE and ÇBP raids that terrorize and divide.
- **Demand** that our tax dollars fund schools, hospitals, and families — not cages, not corruption, not another forever war.
- **Prove** that everyday Americans will protect our rights, our votes, and our freedom.

 We are not watching history happen — we are making it. Our movement is peaceful, united, and resolute. Together, we will shape a country that truly belongs to all of us. Join us.
Presidents serve the people. They don’t rule over us. †®ump crossed that line — and we’re stepping up to draw it back. Rise up, show up, and take back America. **#NoKings**
 
On March 28, the streets will speak. From coast to coast, we’ll rise up shoulder to shoulder and say it loud: 
**No Thrones. No Crowns. No Kings.   **

*A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.*

**[Citizens Against Tyranny](https://www.citizensagainstyrannynetwork.org) | [50501 Joplin](https://www.missouri5050.one/50501-joplin) **

#IMPEACH #CONVICT #REMOVE #WeThePeople #DemocracyNotTyranny #NOKINGS</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/905273/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
