        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS COUNTDOWN Pop-up Protests</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, March 25, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>In front of Carolina Mall<br>1480 Concord Pkwy N<br>Concord, NC 28025</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Cabarrus County</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Help us spread awareness for the upcoming No Kings Rally on March 28th with a a series of pop-up protests at the Carolina Mall location. Bring a friend, flags and signs to let all know we want this to biggest protest yet! There is so much on the line right now, from the illegal war in Iran, the continued corruption of ICE, the SAVE act, etc. Come stand up for Democracy with us!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/919962/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
