<p><strong>When:</strong> Monday, March 30, 2026 at 10:30 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>The Social Space<br>691 John Wesley Dobbs Ave NE<br>Atlanta, GA 30312</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Democratic Party of Georgia</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join the Mid Fulton Dems on the last Monday of the month to hear from elected officials, party leaders, and the community on upcoming elections and events in 2026.

