<h3>SD34 Hossain - Coffee &amp; Canvas</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Braum&apos;s Ice Cream &amp; Dairy Store<br>3126 S 129th E Ave<br>Tulsa, OK 74134</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Oklahoma Democratic Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We’re gathering every Saturday in March 2026 between 11:00 AM and 3:00 PM at Braum&apos;s (3126 S 129th E Ave, Tulsa, OK 74134) to chat over coffee and knock doors for Amy in Senate District 34!
No experience needed—we’ll give you everything you need to make you comfortable and feel at ease!
You can knock doors, have conversations, or just drop lit—whatever works for you!
If you cannot do weekends, let us know, and we will help you volunteer on your own schedule.
Hope to see you there, or sign up to volunteer on your own time at amy4ok.com You can also email info@amy4ok.com with any questions you might have! 


**This event is not affiliated in any way with this business. The business neither sponsors nor endorses this event.</p>
