        <name>NO KINGS, NO WARS - BALTIMORE CITY</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS, NO WARS - BALTIMORE CITY</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Hopkins Plaza<br>1-99 2-98 Hopkins Pl<br>Baltimore, MD 21201</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Trump and the billionaires are waging war abroad while terrorizing our communities at home with our own tax dollars. Racist ICE thugs assault our neighbors while millions lose Medicare and SNAP. Now they push toward a war with Iran while continuing the blockade of Cuba and attacks on Venezuela. We cannot afford any more forever wars, like Iraq and Afghanistan. 

In Minneapolis, thousands of ICE thugs flooded the city in the largest immigration crackdown in U.S. history. The people responded with mass protests and a general strike that shut down the Twin Cities. Now the same federally-backed terrorists are coming to Maryland. That is why we are marching! 

We cannot wait for midterm elections while our communities are under attack. The people have the power to defeat this system, because its power only exists as long as we accept it. 

Join the nationwide call to action in Baltimore.
🗓 Saturday, March 28
⏰ 1 PM.

&quot;A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. 
We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. 
Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.&quot;</p>
