<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We have had enough! Let&apos;s come together as neighbors in Pasadena, say say &quot;No!&quot; to ICE, and &quot;No!&quot; to the immoral Trump regime, and work together to make Pasadena truly a Safe and Inclusive community. 

The Trump Administration has escalated their brutality and authoritarianism on families and immigrants in Minnesota and across the country, killing multiple people including Keith Porter Jr., Renée Good, Alex Pretti, and at least six people in ICE custody so far in 2026. 

Last year, 32 people died in ICE custody, making it ICE’s deadliest year in more than two decades.

Join us for No Kings 3.0 in Pasadena, to tell the Trump regime and their hired thugs -- they&apos;re not welcome here.</p>
