        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Letters for Carlos</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, April 8, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>180 Gordon Dr<br>Exton, PA 19341</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Chester County Democratic Committee</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Chester County Residents in ICE Detention

Carlos Della Valle of Downingtown, PA has been in ICE detention since August 2025. After being transferred 16 times, he is now being held in Louisiana, separated from his family and community. 

Join us as we share Carlos’s story and take action by writing letters and calling local representatives. We need our elected officials to hear us loud and clear: Carlos should not be forgotten, and his family should not have to fight this battle alone.

After hearing Carlos&apos;s story, we will be writing letters to our Representative and Senator to ensure his story is not lost.</p>
