        <name>National Day of Lobbying: Round 3 - From No Kings to Their Offices!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>National Day of Lobbying: Round 3 - From No Kings to Their Offices!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Monday, March 30, 2026 at 2:00 PM UTC - 2:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>340 Commerce Ave 16<br>Southern Pines, NC 28387</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> 50501Missouri</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>On 3.28, millions will gather around the country to say &quot;No Kings!&quot; Two days later, constituents will march their demands directly into the offices of the people who can bring about change: their US congressional representatives.

Impeachment is how the constitution says &quot;No Kings!&quot;

WHO/WHEN:

FLARE USA, Citizens&apos; Impeachment, Sons of Liberty, state chapters of 50501, progressive candidates, and many other concerned citizens will join together in leading constituents into the local/in-district offices of all 435 US House Representatives to demand impeachment and the abolishment of ICE.
 
Please choose which time works best for your community. Late morning and early afternoon times are encouraged. 

WHERE:

Your US Representative&apos;s local office. 

Find your US Representative&apos;s home district office(s) here: https://national-day-of-lobbying.netlify.app/ 

Additional notes:

Please see our full lobbying guide at flareusa.link/lobbywithflaretoolkit. 

Hosts and attendees are encouraged to watch the training webinar from 2.17 at https://flareusa.link/217masscall. 

Hosts are encouraged to request a meeting with their Representative&apos;s office ahead of time to increase the likelihood that they are able to discuss concerns with lead staffers. We will provide you with the email of your office&apos;s District Director to request a meeting. 

Make sure to join the Impeachment Coalition for additional messaging and to connect with other organizers. You can join here: https://citizensimpeachment.com/the-impeachment-coalition/

All actions under this banner are committed to lawful, non-violent action and no civil disobedience. 

By registering for the event, you are agreeing that event partners may receive your contact information and communicate with you about related activities. 

Please contact FLARE USA (events@flareusa.org) with any questions!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/924401/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
