Following the protests and marches of No Kings 3 on March 28th, the Taiba Sultana campaign is launching an important DAY OF ACTION on March 29th!

We will be knocking on doors of residents in Easton and Bethlehem to let them know that there is a new, progressive energy looking to fight working families here in Senate District 18. Taiba is fighting to keep ICE out, halt the increasing buildup of warehouses in our district, bring up minimum wage, establish guaranteed paid family and medical leave, and ensure healthcare for all. Help us spread the word!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/926223/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
