<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Please join Indivisible Lower Merion and members of our community at the Ardmore Citizens Bank branch at the corner of Woodside and Lancaster Avenues on Saturday, April 4th at 11:00 AM as we come together in communities across Pennsylvania to send a message to Citizens Bank and raise community awareness about Citizens&apos; role in supporting for-profit detention operators.
 
