    <Placemark>
        <name>NO KINGS Highland Park NJ</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS Highland Park NJ</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Highland Park Farmers Market<br>212 Raritan Ave<br>Highland Park, NJ 08904</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>**We have the power and are claiming it together. No Thrones. No Crowns. No Kings.**

What began in 2025 as a single day of defiance has become a sustained national resistance to tyranny, spreading from small towns to city centers and across every community determined to defend democracy. Our peaceful movement is bigger than ever.

When our families are under attack and costs are pushing people to the brink, silence is not an option. We will defend ourselves and our communities against this administration’s unjust and cruel acts of violence.

On March 28th, rise up, take to the streets, and say it loud: no thrones, no crowns, no kings. We’re not watching history happen—we’re making it. Join us.

This rally is sponsored by Indivisible Highland Park NJ in alliance with partner organizations focused on defending immigrants, safeguarding democratic elections, and protecting the 99% from economic exploitation by Trump and the 1%. 

We are here to say NO KINGS!  We will not accept a president who thinks he is a king, who uses troops on American residents, steals our democratic right to elect our leaders, uses his office to line his own pockets, and robs from the 99% to cut taxes for the 1%. 

Come to say: 
•	No to ICE being used as a paramilitary force against American residents, whatever their immigration status!     
•	No to Trump stealing the 2026 elections! Protect our democratic rights.  
•	No to Trump and the 1% robbing from the 99%! Stop Trump’s corruption and end the Big Bad Bill’s tax cuts for billionaires financed by horrendous cuts in Medicaid, ACA subsidies, and SNAP food aid. 

When and Where:  March 28, Highland Park NJ, 12 noon to 2 pm.  Meet at the Welkovits Pavilion at the Highland Park Farmers Market at 212 Raritan Avenue. 

Signs: Bring big signs that can be easily seen by passing cars.  We recommend the following: The signs should be at least 2 feet on a side with big letters that are several inches high.  The signs should have simple slogans that are easy to read. Possible slogans:  
•	No Kings! No Trump!
•	ICE: No Masks! No Guns!
•	Disarm and Disband ICE!
•	Trump: Don’t Steal the 2026 Elections!
•	Trump: Release ALL the Epstein Files!
•	Trump: Always for His Billionaire Buddies!
•	Trump: Enriching the 1%; Hurting the 99%!
•	Trump: Hands Off Our Healthcare!
•	Trump: Crypto Con!

*A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/900815/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
