        <name>From Bay Ridge to No Kings 3 with Indivisible Brooklyn!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>From Bay Ridge to No Kings 3 with Indivisible Brooklyn!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 3:45 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>77th Street &amp; 4th Avenue<br>Brooklyn, NY 11209</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Hands Off NYC</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Let’s meet up in Brooklyn to head to Manhattan together to march with Indivisible Brooklyn and Brooklyn Resisters!

We’ll meet on the NW corner of 77th Street and 4th Avenue, in front of the church. From there we’ll take the R train to our meetup spot in Manhattan by 1pm.

Wear your walking shoes and bring your water bottle, but don’t bring a sign—we need folks to hold many beautiful flowers, butterflies and other art as a part of the gorgeous spring field we will be carrying through the march! Please also sign up here for more details and to be part of this powerful work of art: https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblenationbk/event/917478/.

Join us to proclaim to the world: No kings! No war! No ICE!</p>
