        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NYWFP Contingent: No Kings NYC</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Columbus Circle<br>Columbus Cir<br>New York, NY 10019</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> New York Working Families Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join the New York Working Families Party and Youth Working Families Party contingent to say: NO KINGS, NO ICE, NO WAR! We will join millions rising up across the country to make their voices heard! Signs are encouraged but not required.

### Meet-up details 📍 :

- **When**: Saturday, March 28th at 1PM
- **Where**: NYWFP Contingent will meet at Columbus Circle @ 848 Columbus Cir, New York. then we will meet the larger No Kings march at 2PM @ 7th Ave and Central Park South
- **Look for**: WFP signs, and WFP shirts
- **Bring**: Water, a mask, friends, and your WFP gear. 


We’ll gather as the Working Families contingent at **1PM at Columbus Circle** before joining the larger No Kings march at **2PM at 7th Ave and Central Park South.** 

#### BONUS: Catch the Youth Working Families Party pre-march rally at Columbus Circle at 1pm!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/926270/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
