        <name>NO KINGS 3  / Hold Art + March with us !</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS 3  / Hold Art + March with us !</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>POPS (Privately Owned Public Space) Plaza at<br>120 W 55th St.<br>New York, NY 10019</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Brooklyn</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>***Hold Art and March at NO KINGS 3 with Indivisible BK and BK Resisters!***

**PLEASE REGISTER FOR MEETUP LOCATION**

Be an important part of the art for No Kings 3 March on 3/28 in Manhattan!

We&apos;ve created a giant moving art piece that tells the story of peoples&apos; power to overcome tyranny with the unlikely tools of joy and community - and we need you to be a part of it! 

Our warmth melts ICE and the dawn is coming!

We need folks to hold many beautiful flowers, butterflies and other art as a part of this gorgeous spring field! We will also need two strong(ish) people to carry the big WE ARE THE POWER sun.

A few things to note, as you sign up for this:  

1) Arrive at 1 pm, one hour before the start of the march.
2) Don&apos;t bring your own sign!
3) Stick together at the march so we can have maximum visual impact.
4) Return the art at the conclusion of the march.
5) Watch your email for additional information and updates!

Please note: We should have art for everyone - there is a lot of art!  But, hopefully we will get so many people that there wont be enough for everyone - if that happens please understand that it&apos;s a good thing!

Please join us and more to come!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/917478/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
