<h3>From Park Slope to No Kings 3 with Indivisible Brooklyn!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>By the elevator to the 7th Ave. F train station<br>7th Avenue &amp; 9th Street<br>Brooklyn, NY 11215</p>
