        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Hastings Canvass for a Working Families Guarantee</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 29, 2026 at 2:00 PM UTC - 4:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>The Good Witch Coffee Bar<br>134 Southside Ave<br>Hastings-on-Hudson, NY 10706</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> New York Working Families Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We&apos;re hitting the streets to make our voices heard. Governor Hochul - TAX THE RICH!

Join us as we amplify our message by talking with our neighbors in the Hastings-On-Hudson community about the Working Families Guarantee campaign: 

✅ TAX THE RICH
✅ Invest in childcare 
✅ Universal healthcare
✅ Affordable housing
✅ Protect our immigrant neighbors and keep ICE out!

No experience? No problem! We provide the training and the fun. Let&apos;s do this!</p>
