<h3>Indivisible Yorktown We Can&apos;t Afford Mike Lawler Pop Up Protest</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, April 4, 2026 at 2:00 PM UTC - 3:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>2035 Saw Mill River Rd<br>Yorktown Heights, NY 10598</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible YorktownNY</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Our next IY popup will take place on Saturday, April 4 from 10:00 to 11:00AM on the sidewalk at the corner of Saw Mill River Road (Route 118) and Commerce Street, across from the Roma Building, in front of the Mobile station. 

Lawler cut healthcare and SNAP. He increased our taxes through tariffs. He raised insurance costs, gave outrageous sums to ICE and supports a brutal war that raises costs everywhere and risks a recession. 

And now he wants to take away our right to vote!

We can&apos;t afford Lawler!</p>
