        <name>No Kings Rally, Eastern Queens! Saturday, 3/28 @ 11:30 AM</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>No Kings Rally, Eastern Queens! Saturday, 3/28 @ 11:30 AM</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 3:30 PM UTC - 6:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Union Turnpike &amp; Francis Lewis Boulevard<br>Queens, NY 11366</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Chuck for Queens</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Did our country reject the monarchy 250 years ago: YES!
Are we doing it again on Saturday: HECK YEAH!

America has always had complicated history.  From our countries birth some people have used their great power for personal benefit instead of for the good of the community.  Our history of slavery echo&apos;s in ICE raids.   Our history of robber barons echo&apos;s in dark money political contributions.  Our struggle for freedom is not new, it&apos;s a fight we must pick up every day, continuing the work of those before us.

Come out this Saturday to stand with Chuck and the millions of Americans who demand a better country.  

Together we will ABOLISH ICE.  

Together we will get MONEY OUT OF POLITICS.

Together we will take the power from the greedy few, and rebuild a country of the people, by the people, for the people.</p>
