<h3>RESIST Trump RESTORE DEMOCRACY</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:15 PM UTC - 6:15 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>North Adams City Hall<br>10 Main St<br>North Adams, MA 01247</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Eileen For Justice</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Resist Trump!  Say NO to ICE for GOOD.  Stand for Democracy and the rule of law.  Join us at our weekly rally in North Adams, MA.  This week (Jan 17) many people may continue to raise signs and fists against ICE and the killing and disappearing of our people.  But at these rallies, people are invited to bring signs about the issue that moves them most. Enough is Enough!!

You are welcome to stand on any of the sidewalks at this busy intersection.

And a reminder that to keep everyone safe, please refrain from arguing with those who may disagree with us. Thank you.</p>
