<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This rally is an ongoing event to raise awareness for our displeasure with the current Washington DC administration. We will meet each and every Saturday from 10:00 AM - 12:00 Noon, Rain/Shine @ Macy&apos;s in Hampton Bays. There are no speakers planned for now. We ask that you dress warm, bring a chair, a warm beverage, water, snacks/candy to share, friends, fur babies, and children/grandchildren. Costumes, horns, whistles, drums, tambourines, bells, etc. welcome. As always we will maintain a peaceful, loving, environment. We ask that you bring a few items to stock local pantries and/or your checkbook for a tax deductible donation to stock them if you so choose. No cash or gift card will be accepted.

