<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join White River Junction for No Kings 3! As our community involvement grows so do our forms of protest. In addition to a honk &amp; wave we will have music making, a Die In to honor lives lost at the hands of ICE, protest knitting &amp; crocheting, and more! Bring your friends and your family, your signs, percussion instruments (think 5 gallon buckets and sticks!) and stand in solidarity for NO KINGS! 

