        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO THRONES NO CROWNS  NO KINGS</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Rockwall County Courthouse Steps/Intersection of Yellowjacket &amp; S. Goliad<br>1111 E Yellow Jacket Ln<br>Rockwall, TX 75087</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Rockwall County Democratic Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Protest on March 28 to make it clear to Trump that his fear and intimidation aren’t working. In America, we have NO KINGS and power still belongs to the people. Trump is spending billions to send violent ICE agents into our communities. Let&apos;s March together on March 28 to say NO KINGS. 
The Rockwall County Democrats will join our Indivisible Rockwall protesters at their Rally on the steps of the County Courthouse at 1111 E Yellowjacket Ln. and hear our candidates. We will then all join together and March down to the intersection of Yellowjacket and S. Goliad/205 joining other protesters. Bring your signs, pick a sidewalk to protest and let Trump know we the people are not putting up ignoring our Constitution and our Laws.</p>
