        <name>Students Rise Up! School walkout training for May Day</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Students Rise Up! School walkout training for May Day</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, April 12, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Carla Madison Recreation Center<br>2401 E Colfax Ave<br>Denver, CO 80206</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Sunrise Movement Denver Hub</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Organize your school to walk out on Friday, May 1st, 2026! No politician can keep their job, no school can run as usual, no business can turn a profit if they side with Trump and ICE’s violence over us.  Across the US on May Day, millions of workers and students are demanding:
- Tax the rich so our futures, not their fortunes, come first.
- ICE out! 
- Politicians who work for us, not billionaires &amp; corporations.

When we all walk out together, we show the regime they can’t deport and terrorize immigrant communities. Learn more about the history of May Day (https://www.zinnedproject.org/news/tdih/international-workers/) and the history of student walkouts (https://walkout.interferencearchive.org/).

Does your school contract directly with ICE&apos;s corporate enablers? Find out at smvmt.org/riseup, and get the tools you need to plan a mass action on May Day to get your school to drop ICE. Looking for coaching and support for your organizing campaign? Head to smvmt.org/schools-coaching to get connected to seasoned student organizers across the US for weekly peer coaching and register your school&apos;s May Day action here https://airtable.com/appU30eDGp6c12e6r/pagy0W3TjRYf0JVqS/form</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/923783/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
