        <name>Conifer / Aspen Park CO No Kings Day 3</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Conifer / Aspen Park CO No Kings Day 3</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>West Jefferson Elementary School<br>26501 Barkley Rd / Intersection of Barkley Rd and Wolff Ave<br>Conifer, CO 80433</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Hello friends and neighbors. No Kings Day # 3 is happening right here in Conifer on March 28 from 10 AM - 12 noon. Participants should plan on arriving between 9:45- 10 AM however you may join the rally at any time. This is a safe, family friendly, peaceful event. The gathering location is the Ripple Pizza and Ice Cream Parking lot, 26412 Main St. They have graciously agreed to the use of their parking lot for parking and gathering. Overflow parking is on adjacent streets such as Clark Ave, Renaud Ave, Barkley, Main St. &amp; numerous other nearby roadways We will march in unison over the Wolff Ave Highway 285 overpass @ 10 AM, down the footpath and across Barkley Rd. If you are unable or do not wish to march, the West Jeff Elementary parking lot is adjacent to the rally as well as several other nearby roadways. There will be music and speeches. I am looking for 2-3 additional people to assist with safety and security. Also, if you or someone you know has a story to tell about how recent changes in government policy has affected your life, please let me know if you would like to have the microphone for 3 minutes. 

*A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/911083/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
