        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Monthly Fremont County CO Indivisible Community Gathering Potluck</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>The Hive Canon City<br>729 Main St<br>Cañon City, CO 81212</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event!

