        <name>NO KINGS Lake Wales, FL</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS Lake Wales, FL</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 2:00 PM UTC - 4:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Lake Wales, FL<br>451 Eagle Ridge Mall Entrance<br>Lake Wales, FL 33859</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p># No Thrones. No Crowns. No Kings. **WE THE PEOPLE** HOLD THE POWER.

## Join **Indivisible on the Ridge** on Saturday, March 28 in Lake Wales, FL for a rally/sign-waving event to show the power is with the people and we are claiming it together!

***President Trump thinks his rule is absolute, but in America, we don’t do “kings.”***

Since the inauguration, the Trump administration and its enablers are going to extremes to empower the Trump and enrich themselves, all while cutting jobs and services for the rest of us. This administration has killed American citizens, sent masked agents to terrorize our communities, disappeared people off the streets, defied our courts, and slashed services for those that protect the most vulnerable among us—all while orchestrating a massive giveaway to their billionaire allies. This comes at the cost of the American people, our values, and the fabric of our communities. By seizing local police departments, funding mass detention and deportation operations, and pushing for federal control of elections…Americans are witnessing what happens when authoritarians attempt to govern through fear. 

***This is bigger than political disagreement and enough is enough. The American people don’t bend the knee to kings. For anyone who thinks this administration has gone too far, this movement and this moment is for you.***

*We the People* are the majority, and we’re standing together against the abuses of power, cruelty, and corruption. On March 28, join Indivisible on the Ridge in Lake Wales, FL to remind President Trump and his enablers (looking at you Scott Franklin, Rick Scott, Ashley Moody, Ron DeSantis, and anyone working with ICE as part of a 287(g) agreement): **AMERICA HAS NO KINGS!**

***The power is and always will be with the people, and that includes you. Join us in this collective dissent.***

## EVENT DETAILS:
- **Location:** Lake Wales, FL (exact location will be provided via email closer to the event)
- **Date:** Saturday, March 28, 2026
- **Time:** 10:00 AM – 12:00 PM
- **Parking:** Details to be provided via email closer to the event (Event to be held on an accessible sidewalk—email us if you have questions!)
- **Signs:** Pro-democracy, no kings, abolish ICE, demand impeachment…we got 99 problems…take your pick!
- **Safety:** A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. **Indivisible on the Ridge is committed to nonviolence, and we will be taking all reasonable measures to ensure participants’ safety. We also expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. This is a peaceful assembly.**

## THINGS TO DO:

- **Wear:** Comfortable walking shoes, a hat, and sunscreen!

- **Bring:** A sign, plenty of water and a folding chair if you’d like one for your comfort. 

- **Stay alert!** Event coordinators will be available to assist you if you have questions or concerns.

- **Consider volunteering:** As these events grow, we continue to need volunteers to support the cause. If interested in assisting with and/or volunteering for “day of” needs, please email us.  

&gt;## We hope to see you there! We also encourage our members, friends, and supporters to go to additional No Kings events throughout the day in Polk County. Make a day of it, include the kids and grandkids if you can—they deserve the bright future prior generations fought for and _WE THE PEOPLE_ are the _keepers of the flame._</p>
