        <name>Stop the ICE Raids &amp; Distractions: Recuse Biggs &amp; Investigate Names Listed Now!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Stop the ICE Raids &amp; Distractions: Recuse Biggs &amp; Investigate Names Listed Now!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, May 9, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>1752 S Signal Butte Rd<br>Mesa, AZ 85209</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Mesa Valley Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## ⚖️ Stop the ICE Raids &amp; Distractions: Recuse Biggs &amp; Investigate Names Listed Now!



The Administration is using the war in Venezuela and ICE raids as diversions to bury the unredacted Epstein files, shielding the powerful—including Rep. Andy Biggs—from investigation while the DOJ refuses to prosecute a single name listed in the millions of pages of evidence.



📢 **Join [Mesa Valley Indivisible](https://www.mesavalleyindivisible.org/) AGAIN on Saturday, May 9, 2026 at 9:00am** to demand: End the ICE raids and investigate every alleged predator listed in the Epstein Files—starting with Andy Biggs!!


### 🚩Our Demands:

**1. The Full, Unredacted Epstein Files:** Release all 5.2 million pages of the Epstein files immediately. We know the majority are unredacted—stop hiding them.

**2. The Appointment of a Special Prosecutor:** To bypass the conflicts of interest within the DOJ and the Oversight Committee and launch a dedicated criminal probe into every individual named in the files as a participant in or facilitator of abuse.

**3. An End to the War for Oil:** Withdraw troops from Venezuela and cease the regime change narrative.

**4. The Removal of Surge Forces:** End the ICE neighborhood invasions as well as the kidnapping and murdering of our community members.

**5. The Investigation &amp; Recusal of Andy Biggs:** A public hearing on the Sascha Riley allegations and Biggs&apos;s immediate recusal from the Oversight Committee.



### 🚨Important! 

- Please [click here to view additional information regarding Mesa Valley Indivisible&apos;s key concerns](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YuoPvzbOj6KLXZKRWz7QJjQU4VckMmP3N_h26oEET_k/edit?pli=1&amp;tab=t.0) driving the protest.
- Before the protest, please make sure to contact our governments offices and tell them your demands by [clicking this link](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1oDkJ3MY1nNap_fhzK8K8pTSWYg53Vsk9hBXcN0LkER0/edit?usp=sharing) – you will be provided with the contact phone numbers, email, addresses, websites, etc. and scripts for each. 



### 🪧Signs &amp; Messaging
Ideas for signs include: 

✅ Where are the Files?
✅ Abolish ICE. Release Files. Lose Biggs
✅ Release the Epstein Files
✅ Believe Sascha Riley
✅ Investigate the Investigator.
✅ Unredact the Truth.
✅ Protect Children, Not Pedophiles


### 📷 Pictures &amp; Videos
Make sure to always tag **Mesa Valley Indivisible** on our group [Facebook page](https://www.facebook.com/share/g/1CFYV1DSaT/), [Instagram page](https://www.instagram.com/mesavalleyindivisible/), [TikTok](https://www.tiktok.com/@mesa.valley.indiv?is_from_webapp=1&amp;sender_device=pc), [BlueSky](https://bsky.app/profile/mesavalleyindivisi.bsky.social), and [TikTok](https://www.tiktok.com/@mesa.valley.indiv?is_from_webapp=1&amp;sender_device=pc).


### #️⃣ Include Hashtags: 
#MesaValleyIndivisible #AbolishICE #RecuseBiggs #ReleaseEpsteinFiles

### ✨ Protest Information:

- Mesa Valley Indivisible will be at the entrance of the 
