        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Chipping Away At The ICE (Bridge Protest)</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Tuesday, March 31, 2026 at 2:30 PM UTC - 4:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Thude Park<br>2825 W Galveston St<br>Chandler, AZ 85224</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Chandler Gilbert Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>In Arizona, we value our freedom and our families. But right now, federal agents are being used as a weapon against our people, tearing apart the families that make our communities vibrant. It’s time for the Brave of US to show up for our friends and neighbors.

&apos;Chipping Away At The ICE&apos; is our ongoing effort to shine a light on these injustices and demand equal justice under the law. By joining together, we can free our community from the politics of fear and ensure this remains the land of the free.</p>
