        <name>POP UP PROTEST-Palm Springs CA</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>POP UP PROTEST-Palm Springs CA</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 29, 2026 at 5:30 PM UTC - 6:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>SE Corner of Hw 111 &amp; Sunrise Way - Corner of Smoketree Shopping Center<br>1775 E Palm Canyon Dr<br>Palm Springs, CA 92264</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Due to popular demand ;-)) we are back. Peaceful sidewalk protests
Last year we tackled tesla.
This year we&apos;ll focus on whatever you need to say.
Every Sunday
10:30 am - 11:30 am
Corner of Hwy 111 &amp; Sunrise Way in Palm Springs
Starting up again we&apos;ll protest ICE and what is happening in the country now.
We can not remain silent and we know that pressure works.

Bring a chair or stool if you want to, a hat, sunscreen, water, a sign

Please no megaphones or cowbells - we can use our voices but we will not engage with counter protesters. They are unhappy enough as it is.

See you on the sidewalk. PEACE

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
