        <name>NO KINGS Otay Mesa - Birch &amp; Millenia</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS Otay Mesa - Birch &amp; Millenia</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 6:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Birch Road &amp; Millenia Avenue<br>Chula Vista, CA 91915</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>**We have the power and are claiming it together. No Thrones. No Crowns. No Kings.**

On March 28th, rise up, take to the streets, and say it loud: no thrones, no crowns, no kings. We’re not watching history happen—we’re making it. Join us.

*A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.*

----

This is the Event to make it to !   Let&apos;s make it a huge success!  

Invite your friends ... your neighbors ... your family ... your co-workers ... your groups ... 

We will protest at the corner of Birch &amp; Millenia on 
Saturday, March 28, 2026    10 to 11:30 am   (stay tuned for another possible location as well - H and Broadway in Chula Vista time TBD)

**Also, let&apos;s remember to bring any and all pantry stable items for the San Diego Food Bank -- they are struggling more than ever as more and more of our community is being terrorized by ice ... We have collected tons of food this past year -- let&apos;s make this one even BIGGER!**

So, make your plan early - we are going to be having one HUGE Block Party with all of us fun-loving human beings!    

Bring your kids!
Bring your doggies!
Bring your parents!
Just show up and support!

Can&apos;t stay -- drive by and BEEEEEEP loud and long!   That counts as Resistance!
Better yet, drive by and hang a sign our your window in support! (passengers only please!) 

We are Peaceful!

We are also LOUD!

And we are all finally saying ENOUGH!!!!!

See you all on the streets!!

Janine</p>
