        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Indivisible Orange - Picnic in the Park!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, April 12, 2026 at 12:00 AM UTC - 2:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Hart Park<br>701 S Glassell St<br>Orange, CA 92866</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> OC Indivisible (Coalition)</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## Join Indivisible Orange for a Picnic in the Park! 

### We&apos;ll hang out, get to know each other better, eat good food and talk about our plans going forward.

### Date: April 11, 2026. 5pm-7:30pm 

- We will be set up in the green area near the bandstand and tennis courts.

- We&apos;ll provide Hot Dogs, Burgers and all the fixins! Vegan options available. Lemonade, Iced Tea and Agua Fresca to drink.

- Please bring a side dish to share if you are able.

- Bring your lawn chairs or blankets.

- Invite your friends and family!

### Hope to see you there!</p>
