        <name>Washington for All: Sign up for ICE Mobilization Alerts</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Washington for All: Sign up for ICE Mobilization Alerts</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, October 29, 2025 at 7:00 AM UTC - 8:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Washington Indivisible Network</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## **Washington is home. We belong here.**

Working people build Washington. Whether we&apos;re picking apples in the Yakima Valley, fishing on the coast, milling lumber in Aberdeen, raising a family in Tacoma, or running small businesses in Seattle, we&apos;ve earned the right to feel safe and respected in the place we call home.

But, just like in LA &amp; Chicago, the Trump Administration has promised to keep terrorizing cities across America via increased ICE tactical units, mass raids, and deploying the National Guard,  including right here in Washington State. They want us to believe some of us don’t belong here by spreading hate and division. But who really doesn’t belong on our streets? Masked agents who are tearing apart our communities through violence instead of safety.

Trump and his billionaire backers don’t get to decide who belongs in our state. We do.

We are preparing for a variety of scenarios across our state in the event that they escalate their efforts to turn our government into a weapon against our people.

Sign up to know when it’s time for Washingtonians to come together to protect one another.

**We are standing with one purpose**: Together, we will train, organize, and communicate our shared commitment to a free and safe Washington for all.

In preparation, together we will: 

* Train on de-escalation and strategic non-cooperation   
* Make and distribute whistle kits for community defense   
* Distribute information so businesses and individuals know their legal rights

When it&apos;s time to mobilize, we will: 

* Mobilize a unified response
* Advocate for real solutions that meet our needs - like fully-funding our schools, creating good jobs and making healthcare affordable - not wasting our time and money to harass our neighbors
* Focus attention on the ICE violating our rights

### **SIGN UP FOR MOBILIZATION ALERTS &amp; SPREAD THE WORD**

### **We need all hands on deck. Washington thrives when all of us can live without fear, and our success does not come at the expense of others. This is our shared fight.**

A core value of Washington for All is a commitment to nonviolent action.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/868208/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
