        <name>NO KINGS--NO CORRUPTION--NO CRUELTY PROTEST</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS--NO CORRUPTION--NO CRUELTY PROTEST</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 8:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Strands Beach<br>Selva Road &amp; California 1<br>Dana Point, CA 92629</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Democratic Party of Orange County</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>**Danger isn’t just at our doorstep—it’s already in the White House.**

What began years ago as attacks on the media has metastasized into **full-blown authoritarianism and kleptocracy**—a system where **power serves one man and his donors,** while everyday people are harmed.

**While families struggle with rising prices,** Trump made billions through corrupt crypto and foreign-backed deals.

**While people are detained without charges and immigrants sit in jail for months awaiting bond hearing,** the &quot;Epstein class&quot; are let off the hook for their perversions and Trump commandeers the DOJ for personal vengance.

**While healthcare, food assistance, and social services are slashed,** ICE receives billions and pays untrained officers huge bonuses.  

**While American citizens have been injured and killed and peaceful protesters are falsely labeled as domestic terrorists,** Stephen Miller claims ICE officers are beyond immune from the law.   

**While our fundamental right to vote is placed at risk,** Trump rejects election results and threatens to militarize the midterms.
 
**Make no mistake: democracy does not defend itself.**

If we want to keep it, **we have to fight for it**—peacefully, visibly, together.

Join us. Bring friends. Share widely.

We’ll see you in the streets — standing proudly and peacefully for a better future.  

**Ann &amp; Darcie**

Resistance Team Co-Chairs, Democratic Women of South Orange County
________________________________________
**Sign Ideas**

“STOP THE CORRUPTION, CRUELTY &amp; CHAOS”

“NO KINGS. NO BILLIONAIRE RULE.”

“CRYPTO FOR TRUMP — POVERTY FOR US?”

“HOLD THE RICH ACCOUNTABLE”

“FEED KIDS, NOT AUTHORITARIANS”

“DEMOCRACY NOT DICTATORS”</p>
