<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE has been terrorizing our communities by kidnapping our neighbors and it&apos;s up to us to make sure our community members know their rights in these critical times. Thousands of people across California have taken action to defend our communities through protest and sharing important Know Your Rights information but we know that we must go door to door to reach everyone.

