        <name>No Kings Kick Off Party!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>No Kings Kick Off Party!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, March 26, 2026 at 12:00 AM UTC - 2:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>427 Nimrod St<br>Nevada City, CA 95959</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Nevada County</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Indivisible Nevada County for a Civic Action Night Postcard Party and help make our voices heard.

Together we’ll write handwritten postcards to California Senators and members of Congress urging them to:

• Oppose U.S. escalation and war in Iran
• Demand accountability and humane policies from ICE
• Release the full Epstein files and ensure transparency and accountability.

We are excited to announce that District 3 candidate, Chris Bennett, will speak and share context on what’s happening nationally and why grassroots pressure right now matters. This is especially valuable coming from his background as a Veteran. 

Then we’ll take action together.

Postcard writing is one of the simplest and most effective ways for constituents to communicate directly with elected officials—and it’s even more powerful when we do it together.

What INC will Provide:

- Postcards
- Talking points and message ideas
- Addresses for elected officials
- A welcoming community space to take action together
- We will provide some snacks and drinks available for a small donation. 

Bring your friends and your energy!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/915923/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
