        <name>Sunrise PDX General Meeting + Wide Awake Action Training</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Sunrise PDX General Meeting + Wide Awake Action Training</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, April 1, 2026 at 1:30 AM UTC - 3:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>First Unitarian Portland<br>1010 SW 13th Ave<br>Portland, OR 97205</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Sunrise Movement</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>### Time to ACT
In late January, federal agents tear gassed children, the elderly, and union leaders on the streets of Portland. In Minneapolis ICE murdered two community members and continues to kidnap thousands. We will not be silent as they terrorize our communities. ABOLISH ICE. Join our general meeting and Wide Awake Action.

### Agenda 
- 6:30-7pm: Sunrise New Member Orientation 
- 7-8:30pm General Meeting and Wide Awake Action Training 

### Can’t make it? 
- Sign up to organize with Sunrise: http://smvmt.org/pdxjoin
- Join our announcements Signal chat: https://smvmt.org/pdxsignal
- Sign up for email + text updates: https://smvmt.org/pdxupdates

### Who is Sunrise Movement?
We’re building a movement of young people to force this country to work for our generation. We will stop the authoritarian takeover, end billionaire control of our politics, and win an affordable, liveable future for all of us. 

We’re starting by building the power for non-cooperation - so that we can stop the authoritarian takeover of this country. In 2028, we’ll escalate to mass strikes and disruption that force Donald Trump out of power and call for a new political and economic system that works for all of us. In 2029, we’ll end the billionaire-control of our political system system and have a government run by and for everyday people - so that we can pass laws that can stop the climate crisis and make life affordable for all. 

### Sunrise is youth led
Sunrise is movement led by young people under the age of 35. This is to address the reality that young people often have less agency in society and we believe we should get a say in shaping our futures. All our work is coordinated by young people but everyone is welcome to participate in Sunrise trainings, canvasses, actions, and events. 

Sunrise has big plans, locally and nationally, and our new world can’t come to be without YOU.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/751544/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
