    <Placemark>
        <name>Protest Sign Making with Darrin</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Protest Sign Making with Darrin</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 6:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Santa Clara County Democratic Party Office<br>2901 Moorpark Ave #110<br>San Jose, CA 95128</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> States Win South Bay</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Come join the Santa Clara County Democratic Party and States Win South Bay to make signs for the No Kings Protests!  We will have all the sign making materials, bagels, coffee and juice. We are also very honored to have as our guest speaker Michigan State Senator [Darrin Camilleri](https://stateswin.org/candidates/darrin-camilleri/). He can tell us inspirational stories about his efforts in Michigan to resist ICE and protect his community.  

If you want to support Darrin Camilleri in his race to help keep the Michigan Senate blue, feel free to [Donate Here.]( https://secure.actblue.com/donate/sd023-mi-camilleri-southbay?refcode=26MarchNoKingsDay)_100% of your donations will support Darrin&apos;s campaign. We are grateful for all donations large and small!_


_Please note that these events may be photographed and/or video or audio recorded. By your attendance at this event, you agree that any image, audio or video recording of you may be used by States Win South Bay for use in its promotional materials... but we will honor any requests to not be included in photos._</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/914680/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
