        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Weekly San Leandro 880 Visibility Brigade</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, March 25, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 12:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Williams Street 880 Pedestrian Overpass<br>Williams St<br>San Leandro, CA 94577</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Eden Area Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Team Relentless San Leandro invites you to join us each Wednesday and Thursday at the Williams Street overpass that crosses freeway 880 to show your resistance to the cruelty and injustice of the current regime. 

We change the messages to fit current events (e.g Stop ICE Bounty Hunters, Due Process for All, Unmask ICE.) These signs are visible to drivers on 880 and to pedestrians and drivers over the Williams Street bridge. 

Feel free to bring hand-held signs that promote your commitment to non-violent resistance and the values of supporting democratic values of fairness, equal justice and opportunity. 

Bring water, hats, and sunscreen.</p>
