        <name>ICE Breaker - Rally for Immigrant Rights</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Breaker - Rally for Immigrant Rights</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, April 1, 2026 at 12:00 AM UTC - 1:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Courthouse Square<br>2200 Broadway<br>Redwood City, CA 94063</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> The Wolves</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE is a masked, undemocratic secret police force that gives due process the finger and answers only to Donald Trump.

We will not stand by and do nothing while they disappear our community members, leaving nothing but trauma and despair behind. Let&apos;s show everyone in Redwood City and San Mateo County that we stand with our immigrant brothers and sisters in their time of need and we will resist ICE with everything we have.

We&apos;ll meet at Courthouse Square and march through Redwood City. Bring your signs and bring the noise!

This is a peaceful, non-violent protest. We are there to raise awareness, make our voices heard, and have fun. Everything else is none of our business.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/837704/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
