<h3>NO KINGS Redwood City</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 11:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>1250 Jefferson Ave<br>Redwood City, CA 94062</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>No Kings 3 is March 28. Thousands will be out along El Camino across the Peninsula showing outrage at the administration, the illegal ICE actions, taking health care from millions to give tax breaks to billionaires, taking away rights from women over their own bodies, protecting pedophiles--the list goes on. Courage is contagious as we take back the House and Senate AND OUR COUNTRY!

We will meet once again at El Camino and Jefferson in Redwood City as we gather in solidarity and bask in &quot;honk therapy&quot; with everyone driving by joining us in strength and love.

A core principle behind all our events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values. Turn your back and do not exchange words....that&apos;s what they want and will film you as they try to make us look violent.

Love is stronger than hate!

