<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join with like-minded Marin residents to stand up to this murderous regime. We will protest the unconstitutional actions and downright terrorist activities of this regime. We demand **&quot;ICE Out of Marin.&quot;**

This location has bumper-to-bumper traffic going to the beaches and  Mount Tam on weekend mornings.  It’s a great place to engage with drivers and passengers. Our rallies at this location are widely appreciated by passersby and tend to be extremely gratifying for participants.

Please come and bring as many people as you can. If you have signs, bring them.  There will be extra signs.

This is a no-host event. A core principle behind all Marin protest events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values. All participants agree to assume 100% responsibility for their own safety, conduct and well-being.</p>
