        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>CRUSH ICE! NO SECRET POLICE! WEEKLY WEDNESDAYS!! (Waikiki)</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, March 26, 2026 at 3:00 AM UTC - 4:00 AM</p>
