        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO TYRANTS, NO DICTATORS! - LONDON, ONTARIO, CANADA</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Victoria Park NW Gate<br>580 Clarence Street<br>London 96950</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>WE THE PEOPLE have the power and are claiming it together. No Dictators. No Tyrants. No ICE. No KINGS in America! NO MORE!

What began in 2025 as a single day of volunteer-organized defiance has become a sustained resistance to tyranny, spreading from small towns to city centres and across every community determined to defend democracy IN THE USA. Our peaceful movement is bigger than ever!!!

When our families are under attack and costs are pushing people we care about to the brink, silence is not an option. We will defend ourselves and our communities against this administration’s unjust and cruel acts of violence.

On March 28th, we gather to support our families, friends and colleagues in the United States to say it loud: NO DICTATORS! NO TYRANTS!

We’re not watching history happen — we’re making it. Join us. All nationalities, faiths and political affiliations are welcome, in peace and good conscience!

Important Notes: 
The event will start at 12:00 NOON EST (local time).
We will GATHER at the NW corner of Victoria Park.

As Canada is a constitutional monarchy, please do not bring any signage that can be interpreted as disrespectful to our host country.

*A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.*</p>
