        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Immigration Know Your Rights (KYR) Education Workgroup</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Monday, April 28, 2025 at 7:00 AM UTC - 8:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible East Bay</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p># Know Your Rights

The Education Workgroup seeks to support immigrants and allies understand and assert their constitutional rights, especially during interactions with ICE or other law enforcement officials.  We are currently focusing on distributing Know Your Rights Red Cards and Yellow Cards in immigrant and allied communities.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/783161/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
