<h3>GET RESIST ALERTS   Salem/Keizer</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, January 15, 2026 at 8:00 AM UTC - 8:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
