        <name>Host Your Own Powered by Love Gathering: Letter Writing for Immigrants in Detention 💌</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Host Your Own Powered by Love Gathering: Letter Writing for Immigrants in Detention 💌</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, February 4, 2026 at 5:00 AM UTC - 4:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> United We Dream Network</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Over the past month, we&apos;ve watched ICE spread fear throughout our communities, detaining children like five-year-old Liam Conejo Ramos on his way home from preschool. We&apos;ve also seen the incredible resistance of children and parents detained in Dilley, Texas, fighting back from inside a family detention center that should never exist. We refuse to keep watching families suffer. ** Join us to turn this anger and grief into tangible love and solidarity for our immigrant neighbors in detention.** 

❤️‍🔥 Love and dignity for detained immigrants comes from us, the people. It starts with empathy, with care, and with something as simple as a letter. A letter that tells someone in detention: we see you, we hear you, and we&apos;re with you. People enduring abuse and inhumane conditions need to hear voices rooting for their freedom and dignity.

💌 **That&apos;s why United We Dream is calling on you to host a Letter Writing Gathering with your friends and/or family**. Turn your Galentine&apos;s dinner, movie night, or weekly hangout into an opportunity to offer hope and human connection to people who need it most.

Please fill out this interest form to commit to inviting your circle to write letters to immigrants in detention. Join us to be a part of the movement that will build a future without cages and family separation, a future where we will have everything we need to flourish.

🌟 **When you sign up, you’ll receive a link to our toolkit with information on next steps for hosting a letter writing gathering and invitation to get further support if you have any questions!** 🌟</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/897305/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#no_location</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
