        <name>Shut Down Core Civic Phonebanking</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Shut Down Core Civic Phonebanking</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, March 25, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Tennessee For All</p>
