        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Virtual Phonebank</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, March 26, 2026 at 12:00 AM UTC - 1:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Abel Chavez for Congress</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We&apos;re calling voters to let them know about the importance of CA-48 to changing Congress and we&apos;re letting them know about Abel&apos;s bold economic agenda to bring immediate change to every American.  All you need is a phone, we&apos;ll provide training.

Abel will fight for:

Medicare for All, because healthcare is a human right - not a profit center; not “more affordable healthcare,” not “more accessible healthcare,” not “eventually,” not “common sense reform.” Universal healthcare for every person in America, unapologetically.

Ending corporate &amp; foreign lobbying influence, so billionaires and special interests can’t purchase policy or politician’s votes

Banning Wall Street landlords in housing, because homes are for families - not hedge funds

Strengthening public education, so every child has the opportunity for a quality education that will land them a career with zero debt.

Defund ICE.</p>
