        <name>Grow Oregon’s movement for immigrant justice: Sign up to phone bank</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Grow Oregon’s movement for immigrant justice: Sign up to phone bank</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, March 26, 2026 at 12:30 AM UTC - 2:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> PCUN (Oregon&apos;s Farmworker Union)</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us to support our immigrant communities and demand an end to the federal administration&apos;s cruel and unlawful attacks. Across Oregon, we’re seeing an overwhelming increase of ICE and Border Patrol in our communities, targeting our neighbors, terrorizing our children, destabilizing our local businesses, and harming our communities. Now is the time to act.

Phone banking is an easy way to make an impact without even leaving your home. In just two hours, you’ll connect with fellow advocates in your community, invite them to get involved, and help build our collective power.

No experience is needed, and you will receive everything you need:
Training from an experienced organizer
A simple call script
Live support if you have any questions

Together, we’ll invite advocates to take action with Oregon for All, a statewide coalition of more than 100 immigrant justice and allied organizations working together to make Oregon a more welcoming and inclusive state. 

It takes all of us to make Oregon a place where everyone, including immigrants, can live with freedom and dignity. With your help, we can make our movement even stronger.

By submitting this message you consent to your information being added to Oregon For All and PCUN’s database for the purpose of outreach. You have certain rights regarding the personal information we collect about you, including the right to access, correct, update, or delete your information. If you wish to exercise any of these rights or have any questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at mariahinojos@pcun.org</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/915340/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
]]></description>
