        <name>No War in Iran &gt;&gt; Phone Bank to Make Patch Through Phone Calls to Congress</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>No War in Iran &gt;&gt; Phone Bank to Make Patch Through Phone Calls to Congress</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, April 1, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Organizing to Fight Oligarchy / We The Fighters</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE is out of control, ignoring the law and our Constitution, occupying and terrorizing communities, kicking down doors without due process, sending 5-year-old children to detention centers, illegally deporting people and shooting down American citizens in cold blood. 

Join us for this phone bank to urge your Member of Congress to hold ICE accountable.

We will be calling into key Congressional districts to urge voters to make patch through calls to their Member of Congress.

WHAT YOU WILL NEED: You will be need a computer or tablet with internet access and a phone to participate in this phone bank. We encourage you to also bring headphones to help with audio.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/898669/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-03-25T07:02:17.763Z</i></p>
