        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Cancel Hilton, Shut Down ICE: A Booking and Cancelling Action</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, April 2, 2026 at 2:00 AM UTC - 2:45 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Sunrise Movement</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE continues to kidnap our neighbors, tear gas protestors, and terrorize our city. They rely on the support of corporations like Enterprise and Hilton to continue operating. 

Sunrise PDX has been organizing noise demonstrations at Hilton locations where ICE agents have been staying, making sure they don&apos;t get a good night&apos;s rest while they continue to occupy our city. We&apos;re now adding more pressure on Hilton by targeting their bottom line.

On the call, Sunrise PDX organizers will walk you through this direct action --&gt; make (and eventually cancel) a reservation at Hilton to block ICE agents from staying there.

Join us to learn how you can contribute to the ongoing campaign to pressure Hilton to stop housing ICE agents.</p>
