        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>CA3 Gold Country Fighting Oligarchy Monthly Update</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, April 3, 2026 at 2:00 AM UTC - 3:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Organizing to Fight Oligarchy / We The Fighters</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Remember attending a Town Hall last year? Or maybe you signed a pledge after a text banking session in November. Perhaps you&apos;ve done phonebanking with us recently. Maybe you are brand new to activism, and want to take action because you can no longer sit on the sidelines.

There are many concerns: health care, food assistance, education funding, getting ICE out of our communities, and creeping authoritarianism. 

Kevin Kiley has voted for all of these disasterous policies. Help us hold Kevin Kiley accountable.

On this Zoom call, we will hear from local leaders, discuss the current political situation, share stories, discuss ways to take action to ensure Kiley is removed from office next November, and next steps for our movement.

Bring your passion, skills, ideas, commitment, and enthusiasm!</p>
