        <name>RuneHold Workshop: Introduction to DeFi portfolio strategy</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>RuneHold Workshop: Introduction to DeFi portfolio strategy</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, April 11, 2026 at 2:15 PM UTC - 4:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> RuneHold</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>RuneHold provides educational workshops focused on decentralized finance (DeFi), blockchain technology, and cryptocurrency portfolio strategy.

In this session, participants will learn:

• The fundamentals of DeFi and on-chain ecosystems  
• How governance systems like AQUA and ICE work  
• Portfolio strategy and long-term crypto positioning  
• Yield generation through liquidity and voting mechanisms  

This workshop is designed for individuals who want to better understand how to navigate digital assets and build long-term strategies in crypto.

Attendees will receive a structured introduction to key concepts and have the opportunity to engage with real-world examples.

Spots are limited. Register to secure your place.</p>
