        <name>SGV Know Your Rights Phone Banking with AAPI&apos;s for Civic Empowerment - Education Fund</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>SGV Know Your Rights Phone Banking with AAPI&apos;s for Civic Empowerment - Education Fund</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, April 15, 2026 at 12:30 AM UTC - 3:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> We Are California</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE has been terrorizing our communities by kidnapping our neighbors and it&apos;s up to us to make sure our communities know their rights in these critical times. Thousands of people across California have taken action to defend our communities through protest and sharing important Know Your Rights information but we know that having a live conversation is crucial in reaching everyone in our community.

Join us this spring as AAPIs for Civic Empowerment- Education Fund talks to voters about threats to our safety in the San Gabriel Valley such as ICE, housing affordability and data centers.</p>
