<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> AZ LD7 Democrats</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Democrats and Democratic-Leanining Independents from all over our big sprawling Arizona Legislative District 7 for camaraderie, political discussion, and planning.

