<h3>Hope in Action - Monthly Zoom Huddle</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Monday, April 27, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 11:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Action Together NEPA</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Our Hope in Action monthly Zooms are designed to connect Action Together members throughout the region. We cover a lot of geography, but we&apos;re held together by important goals: to build community, to strengthen our organizing power, and to fight for the future that we deserve. 

The best way to face the challenges we&apos;re facing is **together**.  Join us to get the latest news &amp; updates from Action Together and plug into some ways to take action! You&apos;ll have a chance to connect with progressive friends and make some new ones, too. 

📣 As always, we&apos;ll also go over current calls to action, upcoming events, and what&apos;s keeping us all hopeful in these times. Watch for a fun (and mandatory 😂) icebreaker, too! 👀</p>
