        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Whistlemania! LBC Good Neighbor Training - Virtual</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, May 1, 2026 at 1:30 AM UTC - 3:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Long Beach Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for the next phase of Whistlemania! LBC - learning how to be a good neighbor. 

Using the framework of being a good neighbor, we will teach you how to use the tools and alert our communities when there is ICE activity in the area. 

We will go over:

How to identify ICE 

Know what your rights are in this situation

How to use the whistle to alert neighbors ICE is in the area 

How to report ICE sightings using SALUTE

How to film ICE activity

We want to make sure you feel confident and prepared and can teach your friends and neighbors! Please note that this session will be recorded and shared with our members. 

Stay tuned for more extensive training opportunities.</p>
